law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 628, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 373, sec. 6, effective July 13, 1990; and ch. 470, sec. 70, effective July 1, 1990. -- Amended 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 108, sec. 6, effective July 13, 1984. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 399, sec. 10, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 299, sec. 39. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 20.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/13/90). This section was amended by two 1990 Acts which are in conflict. Pursuant to KRS 446.250, the Act which was last enacted by the General Assembly prevails.
